  <div data-qa="course__salary_details">
  <p class="govuk-body">
  You can apply for a salaried teacher training course. However, these courses are limited in number and very competitive. On this type of course, you will not pay a fee, and you can earn money while you train in a school.
  </p>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    You will also need a <a href="https://getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/non-uk-teachers/visas-for-non-uk-trainees">
      visa or immigration status</a> allowing you to work in the UK.
  </p>
